Self.Wiki: Determines the ejection behavior of ejected bullet cartridges.

disableParam_NT.Wiki: Exclude from the NT version or mark the ones to be excluded.

disableParam_Product.Wiki: Exclude from the product version or mark the items to be excluded.

initVelocity.Wiki: Initial velocity of the cartridge. In metres.

initVelocity_RandomRange.Wiki: Random velocity range of the cartridge. In metres.

chrVelocityTakeoverRate_RandomRange.Wiki: Character speed transfer rate. Random range of the inherited speed.

pitch.Wiki: Angle from the horizontal angle reference of the dummy polygon (+: ↑ direction, -: ↓ direction). In degrees.

pitch_RandomRange.Wiki: The random range of degrees for the ejection angle.

gravity.Wiki: Acceleration for the cartridge gravity. In metres per second ^ 2.

gravity_RandomRange.Wiki: Acceleration for the cartridge gravity. Random range of the acceleration. In metres per second ^ 2.

angVelocityX.Wiki: Rotational velocity on the X-axis. In degrees per second

angVelocityX_RandomRange.Wiki: Rotational velocity on the X-axis. Random range of the rotational velocity. In degrees per second.

angVelocityY.Wiki: Rotational velocity on the Y-axis. In degrees per second

angVelocityY_RandomRange.Wiki: Rotational velocity on the Y-axis. Random range of the rotational velocity. In degrees per second.

angVelocityZ.Wiki: Rotational velocity on the Z-axis. In degrees per second

angVelocityZ_RandomRange.Wiki: Rotational velocity on the Z-axis. Random range of the rotational velocity. In degrees per second.

yaw.Wiki: Angle from the horizontal angle reference of the dummy poly (+: right direction of the dummy poly, -: left direction of the dummy poly).

yaw_RandomRange.Wiki: Angle from the horizontal angle reference of the dummy poly (+: right direction of the dummy poly, -: left direction of the dummy poly).
